						<h4>Emily McCrary-Ruiz-Esparza</h4>
												<p>Emily McCrary-Ruiz-Esparza is a journalist and essayist whose work has appeared in <em>The Economist</em>, the BBC, the <em>Washington Post</em>, <em>JSTOR Daily</em>, and <em>Oh Reader</em>, among others. She lives in Virginia.</p>
